        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 11A–B. †Furcembolus spp., left male palp. A Furcembolus longior (SEABRI-Ar003), retrolateral. B Furcembolus martensi spec. nov. (IZCAS-Ar42321Fo), retrolateral. Scale bars: 0.20 mm." ;
